## 🚀 DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS

### **Quick Start (30 minutes)**

```bash
# 1. Set up database (5 minutes)
cd complete-system
psql -h YOUR_DB_HOST -U YOUR_DB_USER -d YOUR_DB_NAME \
  -f database/schema/01-core-enhancements.sql \
  -f database/schema/02-estimating-integration.sql \
  -f database/schema/03-project-lifecycle.sql \
  -f database/schema/04-cost-to-complete.sql \
  -f database/schema/05-enhanced-cost-tracking.sql

# 2. Configure environment (2 minutes)
cp .env.example .env.local
# Edit .env.local with your credentials

# 3. Install dependencies (3 minutes)
npm install

# 4. Deploy application (10 minutes)
vercel --prod

# 5. Import n8n workflows (5 minutes)
# Import contract-lifecycle-automation.json via n8n UI

# 6. Test with NMG project (5 minutes)
# Upload NMG_Buildout_Estimate_UpdatedV1.xlsx
# Verify 48 line items imported

✅ Done! System is live!
```

